#ROOM
Vnum     12000
Name     &GNorthshire Valley - Abbey Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand before the grand entrance of &WNorthshire Abbey&d, a towering
stone structure that serves as the starting point for countless heroes of
the Alliance. Ivy climbs the weathered walls, and the scent of incense
drifts from within. A cobblestone path leads &Ysouth&d into the valley, while
the heavy oak doors to the &Wnorth&d stand open in welcome.
~
Flags    nomob~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12001
Desc      The heavy oak doors lead into the abbey proper.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12003
Desc      A cobblestone path winds into Northshire Valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12013 1 12000
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12001
Name     &WNorthshire Abbey - Main Hall&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     Tall stained glass windows bathe the hall in &Bblue&d, &Ygold&d, and &Wwhite&d
light. Wooden pews line either side of a central aisle leading to a marble
altar at the far end. Candles flicker in iron sconces, and the murmur of
prayers echoes softly. A door to the &Yeast&d leads to the Marshal's quarters,
while stairs descend to the &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12002
Desc      A wooden door leads to the Marshal's office.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12000
Desc      The main entrance leads outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12005
Desc      Stone stairs descend to the cellar.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12015 1 12001
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12002
Name     &WMarshal McBride's Office&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     Maps and reports cover every surface of this cramped office. A large oak
desk dominates the room, piled high with parchment and inkwells. A sword
and shield hang on the wall behind the desk, polished to a mirror shine.
A single window overlooks the valley below.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12001
Desc      The main hall of the abbey lies through this door.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12014 1 12002
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12003
Name     &GNorthshire Valley - Cobblestone Path&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A well-worn cobblestone path winds through the lush green hills of
Northshire Valley. Apple trees line the road, their branches heavy with
fruit. To the &Ynorth&d, the abbey rises majestically. The path continues
&Ysouth&d toward a small vineyard, and a dirt trail branches &Yeast&d toward
a cluster of training dummies.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12000
Desc      The path leads to Northshire Abbey.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12004
Desc      A dirt trail leads to the training area.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12006
Desc      The path continues toward the vineyard.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12012 1 12003
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12004
Name     &GNorthshire Valley - Training Grounds&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Straw-stuffed training dummies stand in rows, bearing the scars of
countless practice strikes. Young recruits spar with wooden swords under
the watchful eyes of veteran soldiers. The clang of metal and shouts of
instructors fill the air. The main path lies to the &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12003
Desc      The cobblestone path leads back toward the abbey.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12012 2 12004
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12005
Name     &xAbbey Cellar&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     Dusty wine barrels and crates of supplies fill this cool, damp cellar.
Cobwebs hang from the low ceiling, and the smell of mildew mingles with
aged oak. Rats scurry in the shadows. Stone stairs lead &Yup&d to the main
hall.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12001
Desc      Stone stairs lead up to the abbey.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12006
Name     &GNorthshire Valley - The Vineyard&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Rows of grapevines stretch across the hillside, heavy with purple fruit.
Workers tend the vines, pruning and harvesting under the warm sun. A
stone farmhouse sits to the &Yeast&d, and the cobblestone path continues
&Ynorth&d toward the abbey and &Ysouth&d into the wilder parts of the valley.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12003
Desc      The path leads back toward the abbey.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12007
Desc      A stone farmhouse sits among the vines.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12008
Desc      The valley opens up to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12007
Name     &GVineyard Farmhouse&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This cozy farmhouse smells of baking bread and fermenting grapes. A
stone hearth crackles with a small fire, and bundles of herbs hang from
the rafters. A sturdy wooden table sits in the center of the room, covered
with the remnants of a simple meal.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12006
Desc      The vineyard lies just outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
