Sector   field~
Desc     The gentle hills of Northshire roll away to the &Ysouth&d, where the
forest grows thicker and wolves have been spotted prowling. Wildflowers
dot the grass, and butterflies drift lazily in the breeze. The vineyard
lies to the &Ynorth&d, and a narrow trail winds &Yeast&d toward an echo ridge.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12006
Desc      The vineyard lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
