#ROOM
Vnum     12009
Name     &yEcho Ridge Mine - Entrance&d~
Sector   mountain~
Desc     A gaping hole in the hillside marks the entrance to &REcho Ridge Mine&d,
long since overrun by kobolds. Discarded mining equipment lies rusted
and broken near the entrance. Flickering candlelight glows from within,
and high-pitched voices echo from the depths. The valley lies to the &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12008
Desc      The hills of Northshire Valley lie to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
