#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12010
Name     &GNorthshire - Forest Edge&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The trees grow closer together here, their canopy blocking much of the
sunlight. Underbrush rustles with unseen movement, and the distant howl
of a wolf echoes through the woods. The safer hills of Northshire lie to
the &Ynorth&d, while a forest path continues &Ysouth&d toward the main road.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12008
Desc      The open hills of the valley lie to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
