Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     Rough-hewn tunnels branch in multiple directions, shored up with rotting
timber. Candle stubs are wedged into cracks in the walls, casting
flickering shadows. The air is stale and smells of unwashed kobold. Picks
and shovels clatter somewhere deeper in the mine.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12009
Desc      The mine entrance lies above.
