Name     &xEcho Ridge Mine - Deep Chamber&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     This large natural cavern has been converted into the kobolds' main
living space. Crude bedrolls and piles of stolen goods litter the floor.
A cooking fire smolders in the center, roasting something unidentifiable.
The stench is almost unbearable.
~
#EXIT
