Name     &xEcho Ridge Mine - Goldtooth's Lair&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     Glittering gold dust covers the floor of this small chamber. A crude
throne made of stacked ore crates sits against the far wall, draped with
a moth-eaten blanket. This is clearly the domain of the kobold leader.
Nuggets of gold are scattered carelessly around the room.
~
