Vnum     12020
Name     &GElwynn Forest - Northern Road&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The road from Northshire joins the main east-west highway that runs
through &GElwynn Forest&d. Ancient oak and elm trees tower overhead, their
leaves rustling in a gentle breeze. Sunlight filters through the canopy
in golden shafts. The road continues &Ywest&d toward Goldshire and &Yeast&d
toward the logging camp. Northshire lies to the &Ynorth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
