Name     &GElwynn Forest - Woodland Path&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     Ferns and wildflowers line this stretch of road. A squirrel scampers
across the path and up a nearby tree. The forest feels peaceful here,
though wise travelers keep one hand on their weapons. The road continues
&Yeast&d and &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12020
Desc      The road continues east toward Northshire.
