Vnum     12022
Name     &GElwynn Forest - Forest Crossroads&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     A weathered signpost marks this crossroads. One arrow points &Ywest&d
toward "Goldshire," another points &Yeast&d toward "Northshire," and a
third points &Ysouth&d toward "Stonefield Farm." The forest presses close
on all sides.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12021
Desc      The road leads east toward Northshire.
~
#ENDEXIT
