#ROOM
Vnum     12023
Name     &GElwynn Forest - Goldshire Outskirts&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The trees begin to thin as the road approaches &YGoldshire&d. You can
see smoke rising from chimneys ahead, and the sound of a blacksmith's
hammer rings through the air. A wooden fence marks the boundary of the
town. The road continues &Yeast&d into the forest and &Ywest&d into town.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12022
Desc      The forest crossroads lies to the east.
