#ROOM
Vnum     12024
Name     &YGoldshire - East Gate&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You enter the bustling hamlet of &YGoldshire&d, the largest settlement
in Elwynn Forest outside of Stormwind itself. The cobblestone main street
runs &Ywest&d toward the town square. Buildings of timber and stone line
the road, and townsfolk go about their daily business.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12023
Desc      The forest outskirts lie to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12025
