#ROOM
Vnum     12025
Name     &YGoldshire - Town Square&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The heart of Goldshire bustles with activity. A large fountain splashes
in the center of the square, surrounded by merchant stalls and benches.
The famous &WLion's Pride Inn&d stands to the &Ynorth&d, its sign creaking in
the breeze. The &Yblacksmith&d lies to the &Ysouth&d. The main road continues
&Yeast&d and &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12026
Desc      The Lion's Pride Inn welcomes weary travelers.
