#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12026
Name     &WThe Lion's Pride Inn - Common Room&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     Warmth and laughter fill this cozy common room. A roaring fire crackles
in a massive stone hearth, and the smell of roasting meat and fresh bread
makes your mouth water. Adventurers and locals alike crowd around wooden
tables, sharing tales and tankards of ale. A staircase leads &Yup&d to the
guest rooms.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12025
Desc      The town square lies outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
