Name     &WThe Lion's Pride Inn - Upper Landing&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors nomob~
Desc     A narrow hallway runs the length of the inn's upper floor, lined with
doors to modest guest rooms. The floorboards creak underfoot, and muffled
conversations drift through the thin walls. A window at the end of the
hall overlooks the town square.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12026
Desc      The stairs lead down to the common room.
