Sector   forest~
Desc     A rocky outcropping forms a natural shelter here, now serving as a den
for the timber wolves that plague the logging camp. Bones and scraps of
fur litter the ground. Yellow eyes gleam from the shadows, and low growls
warn you to keep your distance.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12060
Desc      The forest trail leads back north.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12001 4 12061
Reset O 0 12008 3 12061
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12070
Name     &GStonefield Farm - North Field&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Golden wheat sways in the breeze across this well-tended field. A
scarecrow stands sentinel among the stalks, its burlap face sagging.
The main farmhouse lies to the &Ysouth&d, and the forest crossroads are
to the &Ynorth&d. You can hear chickens clucking nearby.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12022
Desc      The forest crossroads lie to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12071
Desc      The farmhouse lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12002 2 12070
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12071
Name     &YStonefield Farm - Farmhouse&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A sturdy stone farmhouse with a thatched roof stands at the center of the
Stonefield property. Chickens peck at the dirt in a fenced yard, and a
milk cow lows from a nearby pen. The smell of home cooking drifts from
within. Fields stretch &Ynorth&d and &Ysouth&d, and a barn stands to the &Yeast&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12070
Desc      The north field lies ahead.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12072
Desc      The barn stands to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12073
Desc      The south pasture lies beyond.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12018 1 12071
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12072
Name     &YStonefield Farm - Barn&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Hay bales are stacked high in this large wooden barn. Farm tools hang
from the walls, and the smell of animals and grain fills the air. A
horse whickers from its stall, and a fat tabby cat lounges on a hay bale,
watching mice with lazy disinterest.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12071
Desc      The farmhouse lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 12022 2 12072
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12073
Name     &GStonefield Farm - South Pasture&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Sheep graze peacefully in this fenced pasture, their wool thick and white.
A small pond provides water for the livestock. The fence shows signs of
recent repair—gnolls have been testing the boundaries at night. The
farmhouse lies &Ynorth&d, and a gate leads &Ysouth&d toward gnoll territory.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12071
Desc      The farmhouse lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12074
Desc      A gate leads toward dangerous territory.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12074
Name     &gGnoll-Infested Hills&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The land grows rough and wild here, covered in tall grass and rocky
outcroppings. Gnoll totems made of bones and feathers mark their territory.
The creatures have established camps throughout these hills, raiding the
nearby farms. Stonefield Farm lies to the &Ynorth&d, and the hills continue
&Ysouth&d and &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12073
Desc      The safety of Stonefield Farm lies north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12075
Desc      The gnoll encampment lies ahead.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12076
Desc      More gnoll-infested hills stretch westward.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12021 3 12074
Reset M 0 12022 2 12074
  Reset E 1 12012 1 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12075
Name     &rRiverpaw Gnoll Camp&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     Crude tents made from stolen canvas and animal hides cluster around a
central fire pit. Gnolls squat around the flames, gnawing on bones and
snarling at each other. Stolen goods from local farms are piled carelessly
around the camp. The stench of rotting meat is nauseating.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12074
Desc      The hills lead back toward the farm.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12077
Desc      Hogger's ridge lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12021 4 12075
  Reset E 1 12011 1 16
Reset M 0 12022 2 12075
  Reset E 1 12012 1 16
Reset O 0 12011 2 12075
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12076
Name     &gGnoll-Infested Hills - West&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     Boulders and scraggly trees dot these windswept hills. Gnoll scouts
patrol the area, watching for intruders—or easy prey. The ground is
littered with bones picked clean. The hills continue &Yeast&d and &Ysouth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12074
Desc      The hills continue eastward.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12077
Desc      A ridge rises to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12021 2 12076
Reset M 0 12022 1 12076
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12077
Name     &RHogger's Ridge&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     This rocky hilltop is dominated by a massive gnoll who can only be
&RHogger&d himself. The infamous warlord has claimed this ridge as his
throne, surrounded by his most loyal warriors. Bones of fallen adventurers
litter the ground as a warning to others. The gnoll camp lies &Yeast&d,
and the hills stretch &Ynorth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12076
Desc      The hills continue north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12075
Desc      The gnoll camp lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
