#ROOM
Vnum     12080
Name     &GMaclure Vineyards - Entrance&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Rows of grapevines heavy with purple fruit stretch across rolling hills.
The Maclure family has tended these vineyards for generations, producing
some of Elwynn's finest wines. A dirt path leads &Ysouth&d to the main
estate, and the road to Goldshire lies &Ynorth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12029
Desc      The road leads to Goldshire.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12081
Desc      The vineyard estate lies ahead.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12081
Name     &YMaclure Vineyards - Estate Grounds&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A handsome manor house overlooks the vineyard, its whitewashed walls
gleaming in the sun. Wine barrels are stacked near a stone cellar entrance,
and workers carry baskets of grapes toward the pressing house to the &Yeast&d.
The vineyard stretches &Ynorth&d, and a garden path leads &Ywest&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12080
Desc      The vineyard entrance lies north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12082
Desc      The pressing house stands to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12083
Desc      A garden path leads west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12019 1 12081
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12082
Name     &YMaclure Vineyards - Pressing House&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The sweet, heady aroma of fermenting grapes fills this building. Large
wooden vats hold the grape must, and workers stomp the fruit in traditional
fashion. Wine barrels line the walls in various stages of aging.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12081
Desc      The estate grounds lie to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 12017 3 12082
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12083
Name     &GMaclure Vineyards - Rose Garden&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A beautiful garden of roses and flowering shrubs provides a romantic
retreat from the work of the vineyard. Stone benches sit beneath arbors
heavy with climbing roses. This is where young Maybell Maclure often
comes to dream of her forbidden love.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12081
Desc      The estate grounds lie to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12090
Name     &GElwynn Forest - Southern Road&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The road winds south through increasingly wild forest. Defias bandits
have been spotted in this area, preying on travelers heading to and from
Westfall. A path branches &Ywest&d toward Fargodeep Mine. The road continues
&Ynorth&d toward Goldshire and &Ysouth&d toward Mirror Lake.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12029
Desc      The road leads north toward Goldshire.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12100
Desc      The road continues toward Mirror Lake.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12091
Desc      A path leads toward Fargodeep Mine.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12007 2 12090
Reset M 0 12008 2 12090
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12091
Name     &yFargodeep Mine - Approach&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     A rutted cart path leads toward the abandoned &RFargodeep Mine&d. The
entrance yawns darkly ahead, and the glint of candles can be seen within.
Kobolds have overrun this once-productive gold mine, making it too
dangerous for legitimate miners. The main road lies &Yeast&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12090
Desc      The main road lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12092
Desc      The mine entrance beckons.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12005 2 12091
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12092
Name     &xFargodeep Mine - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     Broken mine carts and rusted tools litter the entrance to this abandoned
mine. Kobold graffiti covers the walls—crude drawings and warnings in
their guttural language. The flicker of candles illuminates tunnels
leading &Ywest&d and &Ynorth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12091
Desc      The approach lies outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12093
Desc      A tunnel branches north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12094
Desc      The main tunnel continues west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12004 3 12092
  Reset E 1 12001 1 16
Reset M 0 12005 2 12092
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12093
Name     &xFargodeep Mine - North Tunnel&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     This cramped tunnel shows signs of recent excavation. Kobolds have been
expanding the mine, following veins of gold deep into the earth. Piles
of loose rock and abandoned tools lie scattered about.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12092
Desc      The entrance lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
