#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12094
Name     &xFargodeep Mine - Deep Shaft&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     The tunnel opens into a large cavern where multiple mining shafts converge.
Rickety wooden scaffolding clings to the walls, and rope ladders dangle
into deeper darkness below. The kobolds have made this their main base of
operations within the mine.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12092
Desc      The entrance tunnel lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12095
Desc      A rope ladder descends into the depths.
~
