Reset M 0 12005 3 12094
  Reset E 1 12001 1 16
Reset O 0 12002 3 12094
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12095
Name     &xFargodeep Mine - Lower Depths&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     The deepest part of the mine is damp and cold. Water drips from the
ceiling, and the air is thick with the smell of earth and kobold. Rich
veins of gold glitter in the walls, explaining why the creatures guard
this place so fiercely.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12094
Desc      The rope ladder leads back up.
~
