#ROOM
Vnum     12100
Name     &GElwynn Forest - Mirror Lake Road&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     The forest thins as the road approaches &CMirror Lake&d. You can glimpse
the still waters through the trees, reflecting the sky like polished glass.
An orchard lies to the &Yeast&d, and the road continues &Ynorth&d and &Ysouth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12090
Desc      The road leads north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12105
Desc      The orchard lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12101
Desc      The road continues toward Mirror Lake.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12101
Name     &CMirror Lake - Northern Shore&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The perfectly still waters of &CMirror Lake&d stretch before you, reflecting
the clouds above with uncanny clarity. Reeds grow thick along the shore,
and the calls of waterfowl echo across the water. The shore curves &Ywest&d
and &Yeast&d, and the road lies &Ynorth&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12100
Desc      The forest road lies to the north.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12102
Desc      The shore curves to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12103
Desc      The shore curves to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12102
Name     &CMirror Lake - Eastern Shore&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Willow trees drape their branches over the water here, creating a
peaceful, secluded spot. Frogs croak from lily pads, and dragonflies
skim the surface. A few fish rise to snatch insects from the air.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12101
Desc      The northern shore lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12002 2 12102
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12103
Name     &CMirror Lake - Western Shore&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A small dock extends into the lake here, used by local fishermen. An
abandoned rowboat has been pulled up on the shore, its oars missing.
The tower of &YRidgepoint&d is visible to the &Ywest&d, rising above the trees.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12101
Desc      The northern shore lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12110
Desc      A path leads toward Ridgepoint Tower.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12105
Name     &GMirror Lake Orchard&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Apple and pear trees grow in neat rows across this hillside orchard.
Ripe fruit hangs heavy on the branches, and fallen apples dot the grass
beneath. The sweet smell of fruit mingles with the buzz of bees. A small
farmhouse sits to the &Yeast&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12100
Desc      The road lies to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12106
Desc      A farmhouse sits among the trees.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 12016 5 12105
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12106
Name     &YOrchard Farmhouse&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This cozy farmhouse smells of apple pie and cinnamon. Baskets of fruit
are stacked near the door, ready for transport to market. A spinning wheel
sits by the hearth, and bundles of dried herbs hang from the rafters.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12105
Desc      The orchard lies outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 12014 2 12106
Reset O 0 12016 3 12106
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12110
Name     &GRidgepoint Tower - Approach&d~
Sector   forest~
Desc     A narrow path winds up a rocky hill toward the crumbling remains of
&YRidgepoint Tower&d. Once a watchtower guarding the southern reaches of
Elwynn, it has fallen into disrepair. Defias bandits have been seen in
the area. Mirror Lake lies to the &Yeast&d.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12103
Desc      The lake shore lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12111
Desc      The path climbs toward the tower.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12007 2 12110
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12111
Name     &yRidgepoint Tower - Base&d~
Sector   hills~
Desc     The crumbling stone base of Ridgepoint Tower rises before you. The lower
level has collapsed into rubble, but a makeshift wooden staircase leads
&Yup&d to the intact upper floors. Defias graffiti marks the walls, and
the remains of campfires suggest recent occupation.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12110
Desc      The approach path lies to the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12112
Desc      A rickety staircase leads up.
~
#ENDEXIT
