  Reset E 1 12004 1 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12112
Name     &yRidgepoint Tower - Upper Floor&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This level of the tower is largely intact, though holes in the roof let
in rain and starlight. The Defias have converted it into a hideout, with
stolen crates and bedrolls scattered about. A ladder leads &Yup&d to the
roof.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12111
Desc      The stairs lead down.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12113
Desc      A ladder leads to the roof.
~
