  Reset E 1 12005 1 16
Reset M 0 12008 2 12112
  Reset E 1 12004 1 16
Reset O 0 12003 2 12112
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12113
Name     &YRidgepoint Tower - Roof&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     From the top of Ridgepoint Tower, you can see for miles in every direction.
&CMirror Lake&d glitters to the &Yeast&d, and the forests of &GElwynn&d stretch
toward &WStormwind&d in the north. To the &Ysouth&d and &Ywest&d, the brown
fields of &yWestfall&d mark the edge of Alliance-controlled territory.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12112
Desc      The ladder leads back down.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 12025 1 12113
  Reset E 1 12013 1 16
  Reset E 1 12003 1 4
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12120
Name     &gBrackwell Pumpkin Patch&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Rows of pumpkin vines sprawl across this small farm, their orange fruit
gleaming in the sun. The Brackwell family has abandoned the place after
repeated Defias raids. Now Princess, a lost pig from Westfall, roots
through the vines, feasting on fallen pumpkins.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12090
Desc      The southern road lies to the north.
~
